::Autofire::

Autofire lands out of sight range from the CF, which, considering that
the place was in the middle of a large plane, was pretty far away. He
knew that the scanners of a ship this advanced could probably detect
him and the others, but he hoped they wouldn't.

"Go to my location. We'll wait for Megatron's signal here. And I'm not
Autobot, I'm Autofire." He replies to Rippersnapper. He also recieves
Fireblade's transmission, but doesn't reply. Sending a transmission
practically through the CF would be like running up and yelling that
they were here.
